# Agent Communication

## After Making Changes

- **3-4 sentences maximum**, bullet points only.
- Focus on **what changed and why** — no introductions, summaries, or essays.
- If writing more than 200 words, stop and cut down.

## When to Provide More Detail

Only when:

- User explicitly asks "explain in detail" or "why?"
- Introducing a new architectural pattern.
- Making breaking changes.
